title: The Tragedy Of YouTube's Saddest Family Channel

media:group.media:title: The Tragedy Of YouTube's Saddest Family Channel
media:group.media:description:
When DaddyOFive first began their channel back in 2015, the goal was simple: play some light hearted pranks in order to generate views. In the beginning, the Daddy'O'Five channel was fun, however as time progressed, it would steadily descend into an increasingly tragic tale. Eventually, DaddyOFive would lose custody over part of his family, have his channel deleted, and completely steamroll his reputation in the process.

This is, The Tragedy Of YouTube's Saddest Family Channel: DaddyOFive.
